{"tid":612366,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集結連登力量 四月一日夜晚八點向名校secret開戰（2）","createTime":"2018-03-31T19:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T19:26:59.000Z","uid":144982,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"54fe5de9b73b0d4ca3260f8960637e063d8840b1","tid":612366,"uid":144982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T19:06:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">作戰計劃</span></div></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">四月一日 晚上八點 正式開戰！</span></div></span></strong><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">由於之前我哋準備不足，所以開戰日期改為今晚八點，不便之處，敬請原諒 </div> </strong><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">【未清楚事情始未嘅可以去 <span style=\"color: gold;\">#2</span> 睇返懶人包】</span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">----------------------------------------------</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">速攻 (大約持續一小時)</span></div></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. Instagram 留言</span></strong><br />\n鑑於而家嘅中學生都係用IG多，所以我哋主打嘅戰場會係IG。<br />\nIG account: schools.secrets<br />\n我哋會喺最近嘅幾個post以留言形式黎表達我哋嘅訴求，歡迎大家自行發揮，或者可以用以下嘅懶人包發動攻擊：<br />\n名校secrets管理員極醜惡 曲解投稿內容 事後刪帖欲息事<br />\n事件詳情:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n請大家unfollow此page<br />\n強烈要求名校secrets公開澄清及道歉<br />\n喺IG開新account係非常容易，大家可以開定幾個古人account，或者用真身攻擊亦都無任歡迎。開新account流程如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/180513_672972adae9aa234bfba9e30e1d18c11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F180513_672972adae9aa234bfba9e30e1d18c11.jpg&h=70de8990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. Facebook 留言</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/schools.secrets/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fschools.secrets%2F&d=kB73bLIf%2BAHZVGGCGCQ2qIM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=6f2ec0fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/schools.secrets/</a><br />\nFacebook comment可以加上圖片，所以我哋精心製作咗以下嘅大字報，歡迎大家使用：<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/195958_63ea227a2b4e82b9b029e7490d106a9b.png[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F195958_63ea227a2b4e82b9b029e7490d106a9b.png%5B%2Fimg&d=kB73bLIf%2BAHZVGGCGCQ2qIM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=9d46e3ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/195958_63ea227a2b4e82b9b029e7490d106a9b.png[/img</a><br />\n大家亦可以加上上一段提過嘅文字懶人包，以加強攻勢。同樣大家亦可以開定古人account，準備全面進場！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 檢舉 Facebook Page </span></strong><br />\n(中文版)<br />\n舉報--&gt; 我認為這不應該出現在 Facebook --&gt; 這是仇恨言論 --&gt; 種族或民族 --&gt; 送交Facebook 審查<br />\n(英文版)<br />\nReport --&gt; I think it shouldn't be on Facebook --&gt; It's hate speech --&gt; A race or ethnicity --&gt; Submit to Facebook for review<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 檢舉 Instagram Page </span></strong><br />\n(中文版)<br />\n檢舉 --&gt; 內容不適當 --&gt; I believe this account violates Instagram's community guidelines --&gt; Report account --&gt; Posting inappropriate content --&gt; Hate speech or symbols<br />\n(英文版)<br />\nReport --&gt; It's inappropriate --&gt; I believe this account violates Instagram's community guidelines --&gt; Report account --&gt; Posting inappropriate content --&gt; Hate speech or symbols<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">----------------------------------------------</div>"},{"pid":"f82af7b0015af2a95fa59dc5ae01c944d07bc313","tid":612366,"uid":144982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T19:06:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">長期作戰計劃<br />\n(大約持續24小時)</span></div></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 瘋狂投稿 </span></strong><br />\n投稿link: <a href=\"https://schoolssecrets.formstack.com/forms/schools_secrets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fschoolssecrets.formstack.com%2Fforms%2Fschools_secrets&d=kB73bLIf%2BAHZVGGCGCQ2qIM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=1b7d5677\" target=\"_blank\">https://schoolssecrets.formstack.com/forms/schools_secrets</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋目標係要透過瘋狂投稿去令佢哋於至少一日內無法運作。為咗要令佢哋無辦法輕鬆篩選出廢文，我哋建議大家可以扮認真投稿，例如去佢哋facebook搵啲以往嘅文章，但係del走中間嘅部分，或者喺某小部分鳩打，令佢哋辛辛苦苦睇到大半先發現其實已經被玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n注意事項：<br />\n1. 唔好打粗口，咁樣佢哋例如可以filter by 「屌」，一見到有個「屌」字就成篇文唔使睇。<br />\n2. 唔好打「連登」兩個字，原因同上。<br />\n3. 唔好post重覆內容，佢哋可以remove duplicate posts。假如你有一篇千字文，每次改一隻字，然後再submit就ok。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. PM Facebook / Instagram Page </span></strong><br />\n由於佢哋接受private message作為投稿方法，我哋要透過PM轟炸佢哋去令佢哋於至少一日內無法運作。注意事項同上。"},{"pid":"c4d74b950f145548cf9fbd0f913aa87370f72453","tid":612366,"uid":144982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T19:07:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">名校secrets管理員</span><span style=\"color: red;\">極醜惡</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">行為</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">曲解投稿內容</span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">事後</span><span style=\"color: teal;\">刪帖</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">欲息事</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/184008_6bf675f7f9fc7513531bebb570793826.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F184008_6bf675f7f9fc7513531bebb570793826.png&h=a169ac35&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>事源：<br />\n會員#144982日前向名校secrets IG DM投稿</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/182515_273ab85f1212b1f42c8b3db95e97a4da.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F182515_273ab85f1212b1f42c8b3db95e97a4da.jpeg&h=5c4c84ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>事後於lihkg post:  <span style=\"font-size: small;\">名校secret係咪做緊資訊過濾? <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/610057/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/610057/page/1?ref=web</a></span>發現名校secrets管理員擅自於投稿附圖加上說明<br />\n會員#144982即時向名校secrets提出質詢為何未經許可便加上說明並要求出帖澄清投稿人並無此意</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/182545_a28166ed799d577c124632ea5335feb0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F182545_a28166ed799d577c124632ea5335feb0.jpeg&h=9518e592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/182654_0483b9ff7d8c05f9f81f7bbc079834cc.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F182654_0483b9ff7d8c05f9f81f7bbc079834cc.jpeg&h=5f3512e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>但竟遭管理員無理拒絕 表示不會澄清 更未經投稿人同意刪除該帖</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/182741_8083c439858da6d9d862c3aca7a4bf06.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F182741_8083c439858da6d9d862c3aca7a4bf06.jpeg&h=637003a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>會員#144982再度追問 管理員再三推搪並狡辯稱出帖時經常為投稿內容加上說明<br />\n隨後則對追問已讀不回 打算不了了之</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/182806_4b230f1cea14071def076ded09a239ae.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F182806_4b230f1cea14071def076ded09a239ae.jpeg&h=af0c2035&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一眾會員對名校secrets管理員之醜惡無恥行為怒不可遏<br />\n現嚴正要求名校secrets管理員：<br />\n1. </span><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>闡明</strong></span><span style=\"color: gold;\">為投稿加上說明之</span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">準則</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 為曲解會員#144982投稿一事作</span><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>澄清</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 為曲解會員#144982投稿一事作</span><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">公開道歉</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6f96ed0d54d8d2d11c9a9a14494bb2d99dda0b15","tid":612366,"uid":144982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T19:08:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>同場加映</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">有會員得悉此等惡行後<br />\n向名校secrets管理員詢問其回覆時所得之回應：</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/222603_bd215ba37e4d05e8ec70055d67ab9d03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F222603_bd215ba37e4d05e8ec70055d67ab9d03.png&h=13e364b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/222604_a30eab4ee613ce0330ba568d88661fce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F222604_a30eab4ee613ce0330ba568d88661fce.png&h=1be2008a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/222604_ccb91bd19a0345877a6a06c6030f105f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F222604_ccb91bd19a0345877a6a06c6030f105f.png&h=25c4e9d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">會員 設計窮三代：<strong>本來想比機會解釋下 睇嚟唔洗</strong></span><br />\n原文留言：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/20?ref=web&amp;post=488\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/20?ref=web&amp;post=488</a></span>"},{"pid":"0c4ff95b85f8bd922d0dbdf9419525a6d16c0cc5","tid":612366,"uid":25830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T19:11:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd4d77ce6d420f405249f03825dc0611b32636b","tid":612366,"uid":144982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T19:26:59.000Z","msg":"因為樓主手殘 因此此post已棄"}]}